          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1586955335885-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms have softened, stir through the <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>and<strong> toasted sesame seeds </strong> – this is your <strong>hoisin pork & mushrooms</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1586955340227-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1586955340227-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1586955340227-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1586955340227-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1586955340227-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>lettuce leaves </strong>to the side of your bowl and top with your <strong>brown rice </strong>and <strong>hoisin pork & mushrooms</strong></p><p>Garnish with your <strong>crispy onions </strong>and<strong> chilli rounds </strong>(can’t handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Tip: Make loaded lettuce cups by adding filling to the<strong> </strong>lettuce leaves!</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
